        <div class="msgSubject">Paladin build for Gladiator</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-26 17:13:17   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128813479710545603" id="quote-128813479710545603" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128813479710545603" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=175&amp;mid=128813479710545603&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128813479710545603&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128813479710545603" onclick="followToggle('add','128813479710545603')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
