      <div class="msgContentFrame">Alright looking at a paladin like build for GLD, so far my plan is as follows; <br /> <br />-level Conjurer for Cure, Protect, Shell , shockspikes (spikes for threat generation) <br /> <br />-Pugilist for a second taunt due to the high cool down on GLD's current taunt (don't really see the point of &quot;second wind&quot; in the build besides as a &quot;OH sh*t!&quot; button) <br /> <br />-start with 45 dex and 45 str <br /> <br />-then do a 3 to 1 for vit and mnd  <br /> <br />looking for any other ideas that could improve on the current plan <br /></div>
      <div class="msgFtFrame">
        <div class="msgFtFrameFix"></div>
