      <div class="msgContentFrame">Early on MND is not going to help you out. Put points in STR/DEX. If you start dipping on these stats you will level very very slowly. <br /> <br />MDEF from MND: Not very many spellcasting mobs early in the game. <br />MP from MND: Bone Armillas are better than MND and you can always lvl THau to 16 to get Stygian spikes for mana generation. <br />Other options are Radiance WS Conj(10) which gives you 5% of damage done back in mana.</div>
