      <div class="msgContentFrame">I am planning do be a &quot;spellblade&quot; as it were so I am aiming for these abilities - but I would imagine that even as a tank you might want to look at this line of spells: <br /> <br />Absorb ATK  	Thaumaturge  	18  	Transfers a portion of the target's attack power to you. <br />Absorb DEF 	Thaumaturge 	18 	Transfers a portion of the target's defense to you. <br />Absorb ACC 	Thaumaturge 	18 	Transfers a portion of the target's accuracy to you. <br />Absorb EVA 	Thaumaturge 	18 	Transfers a portion of the target's evasion to you. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 29th 2010  2:54pm by Olorinus </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">AvatarexADV wrote:</div><div class="orig">(I wanna know where Momodi is hiding all these daggers, chokers, chainmail, etc.)</div></div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1616445.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
